WHY DTOs?
‚ùå DON'T return entities from REST API:
- Exposes database structure
- May leak sensitive data (passwords!)
- Tight coupling
- Circular reference issues (User ‚Üí Task ‚Üí User)

‚úì DO use DTOs:
- Control exactly what data is sent/received
- Hide sensitive fields
- Validation annotations
- Decouple API from database

